@startuml sequence_partner_notes
!theme plain
title Add Note to Partner

actor User
participant "NotesPanel(target=Partner)" as NP
participant "NotesController" as C
participant "AddNoteHandler" as H
database "DB" as DB

User -> NP: type, submit
NP -> C: POST /api/partners/{id}/notes
C -> H: AddNoteCommand{TargetType=Partner}
H -> DB: INSERT Note
H --> C: NoteDto
C --> NP: 201
NP --> User: prepend
@enduml
